
BASE.ASH.1.12.97

* set_name(name);
  see 'help set_name' or /doc/mudlib/set_name for details!
* set_long(long);
  what you see when you 'look at' an item.
* set_short(short);
  what you see when you type 'look' in a room or 'inv' or 'eq'
* set_weight(weight);
  how much the item weighs.     'help set_weight'
* set_value(value);
  how much value the item has.  'help set_value' 


